Package: funchir
Version: 0.2.0
Title: Convenience Functions by Michael Chirico
Author: Michael Chirico
Maintainer: Michael Chirico <MichaelChirico4@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
Description: YACFP (Yet Another Convenience Function Package). Examples are get_age(), which is a fast & accurate tool for measuring fractional years between two dates; abbr_to_colClass(), which is a much more concise way of feeding many types to a colClass argument in a data reader; and stale_package_check(), which tries to identify any library() calls to unused packages
Imports: data.table, jsonlite
Suggests: testthat
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/MichaelChirico/funchir
